mana, a valiant one and enhancer of glory, who was shy of praising him, Rama lovingly, forcibly drawing him onto his lap and making him sit on examined again and again the wounded body and looked at him.","words":[{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"valiant"},{"d":"कीर्तिवर्धनम्","m":"enhancer of glory"},{"d":"तंलक्ष्मणम्","m":"him, Lakshmana"},{"d":"शिरसि","m":"head"},{"d":"उपाघ्राय","m":"bending"},{"d":"लज्जमानम्","m":"shy"},{"d":"स्नेहात्","m":"lovingly"},{"d":"बलात्","m":"forcibly"},{"d":"आरोप्य","m":"drawing"},{"d":"तंलक्ष्मणम्","m":"that Lakshmana"},{"d":"उपवेश्य","m":"making him sit"},{"d":"अवपीडतम्","m":"wounded"},{"d":"परिष्वज्य","m":"examining"},{"d":"स्निग्धम्","m":"red"},{"d":"उदैक्षत","m":"looked at him"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"शल्यसंपीडितंशस्तंनिःश्वसन्तंतुंलक्ष्मणम् ।रामस्तुदुःखसन्तप्तंतंतुनिःश्वासपीडितम् मूर्ध्निचैनमुपाघ्रायभूयःसंस्पृश्य च त्वरन् ।उवाचलक्ष्मणंवाक्यमाश्वास्यपुरुषर्षभः","trans":"Lakshmana, a bull among men, body tormented by arrows, immersed in pain, breathing heavily. Rama stroking him, restoring his confidence, quickly spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"पुरुषर्षभः","m":"bull among men"},{"d":"शल्यसम्पीडितम्","m":"tormented body arrows"},{"d":"शस्तम्","m":"by arrows"},{"d":"निःश्वसन्तम्","m":"breathing heavily"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"दुःखसन्तप्तम्","m":"immersed in pain"},{"d":"निःश्वासपीडितम्","m":"breathing hard"},{"d":"तम्","m":"him"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"संस्पृश्य","m":"stroking him"},{"d":"आश्वास्य","m":"restoring his confidence"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"शल्यसंपीडितंशस्तंनिःश्वसन्तंतुंलक्ष्मणम् ।रामस्तुदुःखसन्तप्तंतंतुनिःश्वासपीडितम् मूर्ध्निचैनमुपाघ्रायभूयःसंस्पृश्य च त्वरन् ।उवाचलक्ष्मणंवाक्यमाश्वास्यपुरुषर्षभः","trans":"Lakshmana, a bull among men, body tormented by arrows, immersed in pain, breathing heavily. Rama stroking him, restoring his confidence, quickly spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"पुरुषर्षभः","m":"bull among men"},{"d":"शल्यसम्पीडितम्","m":"tormented 